                                                    java.lang.String transferMethodCurrency,

                                                    java.lang.String transferMethodProfileType)
        Creates new instance of AddTransferMethodFragment this is the proper initialization of this class since the default constructor is reserved for android framework when lifecycle is triggered. The parameters in newInstance(String, String, String, String) is mandatory and should be supplied with correct data or this fragment will not initialize properly.
        Parameters:
        transferMethodCountry - the country selected when creating transfer method
        transferMethodCurrency - the currency selected when creating transfer method
        transferMethodType - the type of transfer method needed to create transfer method
        transferMethodProfileType - the type of transfer method profile needed to create transfer method
